## Styling

- Tailwind v4 is configured (see `postcss.config.mjs` and `globals.css`)
- Use the `cn` helper from [`lib/utils.ts`](mdc:lib/utils.ts) to merge classes
- Prefer semantic wrappers and composable primitives (Radix UI)
- Keep component class names small; extract variants with `class-variance-authority`
- Avoid inline styles; prefer Tailwind utilities and CSS variables in `globals.css`